name: Deceptively Simple #007
description:
This is #007 of "Deceptively Simple"

The following generative series is a set of 10 unique pieces that at first glance are simple geometrical shapes with a compelling color palette. Yet when looking closer every shape is made up of small ovals that are layered in a very specific pattern. Some of the ovals are spread out more, others are different shades, transparent and variations of each color.

The piece is 5000x5000 in order to ensure the ability to display on larger displays.

On Twitter: @generatecoll / Instagram: @generate.collective (2021)
